LIMITED PERMISSIONS

Subject to the conditions of this license, permission is granted, free of
charge, to any person to:

1. VIEW AND FORK ON GITHUB. View the source code of the official repository
   (https://github.com/Nitsu430/Bannerbound) and fork it within GitHub solely
   for the purposes of reading the code and preparing contributions (pull
   requests) to the official repository.

2. PERSONAL USE. Compile the Mod from the official repository and use official
   release builds for playing Minecraft, including on multiplayer servers you
   play on or operate. Players and server operators must obtain the Mod from
   the official repository or official project pages.

3. MODPACKS. Include unmodified official release files of the Mod in modpacks,
   provided the modpack is distributed free of charge and the Mod is credited
   as "Bannerbound" with a link to the official repository or an official
   project page.

